

                           [help stop]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------   

Usage: 'stop hunting'

  This command is used to stop hunting a fleeing player. When you are
  hunting, each time you enter the room a fight will ensue, by using 
  this command you will not attack. 
  NOTE: You cannot stop being hunted, others will still hunt you
        until they use this command or a certain amount of time
        elapses.

